To use this flat constitution template, just replace the names in the preamble.
The constitution should scale well to living communities of significantly bigger sizes than ours is. 

```
We the people, defined as [insert your names here], are establishing a living community.
To keep order and peace within aforementioned living community, we ordain and establish this Constitution.
```

You may fork this repo and change anything you want in the constitution, just make sure to include the
license and notice in your fork.

For this constitution to come into effect, make sure to sign and frame it. 
